## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d9eba-166"><xref:System.Net.Http.HttpClient> 한 번 인스턴스화되면 응용 프로그램의 수명 내내 다시 사용 될 것입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d9eba-166"><xref:System.Net.Http.HttpClient> is intended to be instantiated once and re-used throughout the life of an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d9eba-167">모든 요청에 대 한 HttpClient 클래스를 인스턴스화 과도 한 부하에서 사용 가능한 소켓 수가 소진 되어 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d9eba-167">Instantiating an HttpClient class for every request will exhaust the number of sockets available under heavy loads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d9eba-168">그러면 SocketException 오류입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d9eba-168">This will result in SocketException errors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d9eba-169">다음은 올바르게 HttpClient를 사용 하는 예제입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d9eba-169">Below is an example using HttpClient correctly.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public class GoodController : ApiController  
{  
    // OK  
    private static readonly HttpClient HttpClient;  
  
    static GoodController()  
    {  
        HttpClient = new HttpClient();  
    }  
}  
  
```
